2D and 3D Coordinate Rotation

(x, y)→rotate by angle →(x1, y1)

x1 = x.cos(angle) - y.sin(angle);
y1 = y.cos(angle) + x.sin(angle);

例：座標を0.5度回転させると(5, 3)はどこに移動するか？
x1 = 5 * cos(0.5) - 3 * sin(0.5);
y1 = 3 * cos(0.5) + 5 * sin(0.5);

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rotation_(mathematics)


その軸を回転させるか決める
z軸を回転させると
x, y座標が動く

x axis Rotation
y1 = y.cosA - z.sinA
z1 = z.cosA + y.sinA

y axis Rotation
x1 = x.cosA - z.sinA
z1 = z.cosA + x.sinA

z axis Rotation
x1 = x.cosA - y.sinA
y1 = y.cosA + x.sinA

